{"tid":1596743,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"我地唔只話要真普選咁簡單","createTime":"2019-09-26T15:36:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-27T12:34:55.000Z","uid":116374,"like":29,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"e840943373a4da6fe313405d9385cc7b27925316","tid":1596743,"uid":116374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T15:36:53.000Z","msg":"政府依加好明顯想成立獨立調查委員會<br />\n我地要做既唔係剩係要講真普選有幾重要咁簡單<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">而係要有個實際既真普選schedule同埋format </span></strong></span><br />\n一味講真普選有幾重要其實好多人都唔會理你<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>因為好多人會覺得依件事好難同埋好遙遠</strong></span></span><br />\n所以我地依加要做既野係<br />\n1.set個deadline 同政府講幾時之前要有雙普選<br />\n2.諗同埋傾點樣為之真普選<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>只要內容越實際 d人就覺得越可行 先會有越多人支持我地</strong></span></span><br />\n岩岩個會有個藍絲話未來係我地既 <br />\n要我地為自已既未來負責<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">就等我地用行動話比佢地知我地想要一個點既未來<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"e2b67f6d2f432d0316afaaed79047a0111f17ad0","tid":1596743,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T15:40:57.000Z","msg":"push<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n[文宣] 我哋好似忘記咗其中一條重要戰線<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1592692\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1592692</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"49415db83ea24ecd7d9cc9b32a62b076c60d0a8a","tid":1596743,"uid":116374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T15:46:40.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"546b72765da3b59f447ed4c2b6650abf2b8d769e","tid":1596743,"uid":282777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T15:47:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7152a553bae7e8de43fd7a1bbd8d83ad9891dff2","tid":1596743,"uid":282777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T15:47:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"